    <item>
      <title>南非团结政府各政党支持经济快速增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/south-africa-unity-government-parties-back-rapid-economic-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非非洲人国民大会和民主联盟在组建所谓的民族团结政府的协议中承诺实现“快速、包容和可持续”的经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/south-africa-unity-government-parties-back-rapid-economic-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 11:49:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场对南非走向广泛政府联盟的举措表示欢迎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/markets-cheer-south-africa-s-move-to-broad-government-alliance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非股市上涨，兰特上涨，不受全球风险资产抛售的影响，因为投资者对敌对政党达成协议、支持西里尔·拉马福萨连任总统感到高兴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/markets-cheer-south-africa-s-move-to-broad-government-alliance</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 11:27:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国左翼公布计划，推翻马克龙改革并藐视欧盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/french-left-unveils-plan-to-undo-macron-s-reforms-and-defy-eu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国左翼政党联盟提出一份宣言，批评总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙七年来实施的大部分经济改革，并使法国在财政政策问题上与欧盟发生冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/french-left-unveils-plan-to-undo-macron-s-reforms-and-defy-eu</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:37:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
