      <title>教皇首次出席 G7 峰会之际，一场关于 LGBTQ 权利的争吵爆发</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/g7-summit-pope-francis-visit-prompts-negotiations-on-abortion-trans-rights</link>
